          <p class='first-para'>
            <span class="italic">rose&#x2014;</span>
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0411P0_20031016_WH_21'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-andrew-bennett' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0411P0_20031016_WH_21' title='Link to this speech by Mr Andrew Bennett' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-andrew-bennett" title="Mr Andrew Bennett">Andrew Bennett</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            Does my hon. Friend want to intervene?
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0411P0_20031016_WH_22'>  </a>
        <blockquote class='contribution_text entry-content'>
