        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-jim-cousins' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0411P0_20031016_WH_88' title='Link to this speech by Mr Jim Cousins' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-jim-cousins" title="Mr Jim Cousins">Mr. Cousins</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            I am very grateful to the Minister, and it is a credit to the masterly strategy of Mr. Deputy Speaker, who is in charge of us, that we are able to do this.</p><p>
            I would press the Minister on that point. If there is not a target for every region but for regions smoothed together, and if we do not know the outcome of the measure until 2010 or 2014, is it not a meaningless exercise?
